            "title": "盤中速報 - 萊迪思半導體(LSCC-US)大漲5.01%，報117.49美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>萊迪思半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:LSCC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/LSCC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">LSCC-US</a>)截至台北時間17日21:51股價上漲5.61美元，報117.49美元，漲幅5.01%，成交量213,075（股），盤中最高價117.49美元、最低價113.49美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+1.43%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.85%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+1.06%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.32%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>萊迪思半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:LSCC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/LSCC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">LSCC-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+5.26%</li> <li>近 1 月：+24.42%</li> <li>近 3 月：+34.44%</li> <li>近 6 月：+59.37%</li> <li>今年以來：+52.05%</li></ul></section></main>",
